Text: CLT SuperConference Cc Jamespst The Corporate Legal Times SuperConference is fast approaching Arthur Andersen and Andersen Legal are cosponsoring this exciting conference on June at the Hyatt Regency in Chicago The focus of this SuperConference is on management issues facing Corporate Counsel with sessions revolving around seven general topics The program will address the following Optimizing Risk Maximizing the Value of Intellectual Capital Leveraging Human Capital Making the New Economy Your Departments Operating Model Enhancing Your Performance Managing Outside Counsel and Other Service Providers Being a Proactive Business Partner Please refer to the following address on the Internet to view the invitation CLT For more information on the event or to register please visit SuperConference FREE The Worlds Best Email Address emailcom Reserve your name now at
